</description><media:thumbnail url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/35118240-f9bf-11eb-b25a-005056bf30b7/w:1024/p:16x9/AP21221672275189.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/35118240-f9bf-11eb-b25a-005056bf30b7/w:1024/p:16x9/AP21221672275189.jpg" type="image/jpeg" length="0"/><guid isPermaLink="false">c0a54472-f9bf-11eb-a6a8-005056a9d413</guid><pubDate>Tue, 10 Aug 2021 09:45:49 GMT</pubDate><source url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/35118240-f9bf-11eb-b25a-005056bf30b7/w:1024/p:16x9/AP21221672275189.jpg">© AP - Andrei Stasevich攝影</source><dc:creator>呢喃</dc:creator></item><item><category>生態</category><title>新冠病毒變種多：BioNTech的創始人傾向於第三劑量而不是新疫苗</title><link>https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E7%94%9F%E6%85%8B/20210810-%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E8%AE%8A%E7%A8%AE%E5%A4%9A-biontech%E7%9A%84%E5%89%B5%E5%A7%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%82%BE%E5%90%91%E6%96%BC%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%8A%91%E9%87%8F%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%96%B0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97</link><description>
